import React from "react";
import {
  Container,
  Form,
  UserImg,
  UserInfo,
  UserText,
  UserTextBox,
  Wrap,
} from "./styled";
import {
  Button,
  ContentContainer,
  Hr,
  Input,
  Label,
  Title,
} from "src/commonStyles";

export default function PersonalCabinet() {
  return (
    <Wrap>
      <ContentContainer>
        <Title>Личный кабинет</Title>
        <Hr />
        <UserInfo>
          <UserImg $backgroundImg="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1633332755192-727a05c4013d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8Mnx8dXNlcnxlbnwwfHwwfHx8MA%3D%3D&w=1000&q=80" />
          <UserTextBox>
            <UserText>Иванов Иван</UserText>
            <UserText>id:123</UserText>
          </UserTextBox>
          <Form>
            <Container>
              <Label>Имя</Label>
              <Input />
            </Container>
            <Container>
              <Label></Label>
              <Input />
            </Container>
            <Container>
              <Label></Label>
              <Input />
            </Container>
            <Container>
              <Label></Label>
              <Input />
            </Container>
            <Container>
              <Label></Label>
              <Input />
            </Container>
            <Button type="submit">Сохранить</Button>
          </Form>
        </UserInfo>
      </ContentContainer>
    </Wrap>
  );
}
